Detailed Description

cvmx_sriomaint::_ir_pi_phy_stat

This register displays the status of the link initialization state machine. Changes to this state cause the SRIO()_INT_REG[LINK_UP] or SRIO()_INT_REG[LINK_DOWN] interrupts.
